verse:
. Ewuradze yε Nyame ampa;
Ͻnoara na ᴐyεε hεn;
Yεyε Nedze, ᴐnyεn hεn daa;
N’edzidzibea do nguan nye hεn.

. O hom nhεn N'aponkεse mu;
Hom mbedzi dεw N'abanguado;
Hom nyhira N', nyi Ne dzin ayεw;
Na hεn Nyame fata ndaase:

. Osiandε Ewuradze yε pa;
N'ehumbᴐbᴐr so tsim hᴐ daa;
No nokwardzi si pi ampa,
Na ᴐnnkᴐbᴐ adze ara da.	Amen.

. HOM nkotow Hen nyimnyamfo a ɔwɔ sor;
Mfa ndaase nkamfo No tum nye No dɔ;
Hɛn kyɛm nye hɛn Gyefo, Mbersantsen Panyin,
Ahoɔfɛw nye No buw, ayɛyi abɔ N' do.

. Ɔhwɛ hɛn, dze fir hɛn dɛ egya; 
Onyim hɛn mberɛwyɛ dodow;
Ɔma hɛn do dɔ mu ara,
Ɔgye hɛn atamfo nyina nsam',
Yi No ayɛw!
Dɛ mbrɛ N' adom pem mber nyina.

. Krɔnkrɔn mprɛnsa, Egya, Sunsum Ba; 
Nyametsir nwanwa, Ɔkorsa,
Abɔn yɛkotow W' egua enyim;
Adom, fafir, nkwa, fa dom hɛn.    Amen.

. Mo pon so Ɔwo ewie to 
Wɔ m' atamfo enyim;
Edze seradze asera me tsirm';
Mo kuraba ebu do.

. Ayɛyi nka Ewuradze, Tumfo, abɔdze nyina hen; 
O me kra, yi N' ayɛw, Ɔno nye w' ahom na nkwagye;
Hom a hom tse,
Enuaam na nkyerɛbaa, hom mbra,
Hom ntonton No enyigye mu.

. 'Wo na eto pon wɔ m' enyim; 
Ihue adom gu mo do;
Ao, enyigye bɛn na ofi
Wo kuraba mu bu do!

. W' adom tsen du obiara do, 
Na onnyi mbanano;
Ɔto adasamba nyina;
Ɔwɔ hɔ afebɔɔ.

. Mo mfom nyinii dur sorsor no; 
W' ehumbɔbɔr traa hɔ;
Christ no mu edoom me fakyɛ,
Fakyɛ a wɔnnto n' abaw.

. Nkorɔfo nyina nhua Jesus dzin; 
Abɔfo nhwe No fam';
Wɔmfa ahenkyɛw no mbra mbɔsoa N',
Na wɔnhyɛ N' abɔso Hen.

. Wo nokwar si pi, ɔnnsakyer; 
Nyia ɔfrɛ Wo n' egye no nkwa;
Iye ma nyia ɔhwehwɛ Wo,
Nyia ohu Wo n' N' adze nyina.

. Nyame mu Nyame, 
Kan a ofir Kan mu,
Hwɛ! oennkyir ɔbaabun n' awotoa;
Nyame ara ampa,
Wɔwoo N', na wɔannyɛ No;
O hom mbra mma yɛntonton Ewuradze Christ.

. O Christianfo, hom nnyan na adze akye, 
Anapa yi na wɔwoo Agyenkwa;
Hom nsoɛr na hom ntonton Nyame dɔ,
Esumasɛm a abɔfo tow ho ndwom;
Hɔn na wodzii kan kaa n-sɛmpa no,
Mbrɛ Nyame bɛbrae ma ɔbaabun woo N'.

. N' adasoe do na bɔw rososɔ hyɛnhyɛnn; 
Nantwibuwm' na ɔdze Ne tsir ato komm;
Ɔda hɔ n' abɔfo ruhuahua no dɛ,
Adasa Yɛfo, Ɔhen na Gyefo.

. Hɛn ayɛyɛdze piigyan nyina nnsɛ hwee; 
Akyɛdze biara nntum nnya N' enyimpa;
Akomam' ndaase na abɔbɔfo mpaabɔ
Som bo kɛsekɛse ma Onyame.

. Ewuradze, fa Wo kan bra, 
Gyedzi a otu hɛn suro no a;
Ma Wo dɔ nkitsa hɛn 'koma,
Gya hɛn kɔ W' asomdwee kwan mu;
Hɛn akra a wosuro wu dzen,
Gya hɔn twa no sunsuma mu.

. Wodze Guanhwɛfo n' abɔ afɔr ama nguan n'; 
Akowaa ayɛ bɔn, Ba n' agye ho ntsea;
Ber a nyimpa noara no nkwagye nnyɛ n' asɛm,
Nyankopɔn per no.

. Hom mbra ma yɛnka mmɔm kakra; 
Hom mbra Agyenkwa Ne nkyɛn ha;
Hom mbra ma yɛmbɔm', yɛnka mmɔm:
Hɛn Wura Jesus, wɔabɔ N' mbeamuduam.

. Ne mbeamudua n' yi hɛn afɔdzi; 
Ɔtaa hɔn a wɔtɔ bitsi;
Ɔhyɛ hɛn dzen mbusu ber mu;
Ɔma dza ɔyɛ wen yɛ dɛw.

. Ɔma ohufo mbanyinndam; 
Ɔhyɛ okotoo dzen ma ɔko;
Ɔma kan hyerɛn hɛn wumpa do,
Mma yennsuro samanadze.

. Wɔakrɔn hɛn Wura Christ wɔ sor;
Alleluia!
Yedzi N'ekyir rokɔ hɔ;
Alleluia!
Yɛtse dɛ Ɔno a, yɛbɔsoɛr;
Alleluia!
Mbeamudua n' nye sor man n' hɛndze a:
Alleluia!

. Ewuradze Christ asoɛr bio; 
Christ ebubu mpokyerɛ nyinam';
Tsie, abɔfo robɔ se,
Rotow ndwom wɔ sor daa daa:
                          Hallelujah!

. Ɔko kɛse no abɔ adze; 
Afei hɛn Sahen edzi nyim;
Wɔnhyɛ ehurusi ndwom n' ase: 
	Alleluia!

. Aweɛhow ndaansa no etwam'; 
Ɔasoɛr konyim mu efi wum';  
Enyimnyam nka Hen tseasefo n'; 
	Alleluia!

. Dzi dɛw, Nyame yɛ Hen! 
Kotow w' Ewuradze;
Ɔdasanyi, tow ndwom,
Na dzi dɛw daa nyina:

   Ma w' akoma nye wo ndze do; 
   Dzi dɛw, mese wo dɛ, Dzi dɛw.

. N' ahendzi mmbɔ adze da, 
No tum wɔ sor na ase;
Wɔdze samandze;
Saafee ama Jesus:

. N' amandzehu ho nsɛnkyerɛdze 
Da ho ara wowɔ No ho;
Dza N' asomfo a wɔapon hɔn no
Dzi ho ehurusi daa n';
Yɛdze dɛw bɛn
Bɔhwɛ enyimnyam etua n'.

. Mbrɛ odzi hen n', nhyira ahyɛ ma, 
Wotu adaduafo apo;
Afonafo nya daa ahomka;
Na ehiafo so, wohyira hɔn.

. Siar Ewia! yɛserɛ Wo, pue;
Fa Wo kan nye Wo ntseasee
Hyɛ agyedzifo mu ma.

. KANEÀ a yɛdze hwɛ hɛn kwan mu,
Mma yaammfom kwan yɛannyew;
Adom n-sù a ofi sor tɔ
Ma akwantufo nom bi;

. Mma mmpa mo ho, Agyenkwa brɛfo, 
Ma mondɔ Wo na mentar Wo;
Mo kɔn adɔ W' enyimtsewee;
Ber a 'refrɛ yi frɛ me so,

. Bra, ɔbɛma W' ahomgye; 
Twer No: N' asɛm si no pi:
Ɔgye abɔn mu abɔn;
Christ ɔgye ndzebɔnyɛfo.

. Abɔn, 'kɔbesaefo, hom mbra, 
Bahatɔfo, epirafo,
Jesus rotweɔn agye hom nkwa;
Tsema na tum ahyɛ N' ma;
Ɔyɛ Tumfo
Ɔpɛ, mma hom nngye kyim bio.

. Hom mbra, hom a hom kɔn ebu, 
Hom a asehwe epira hom;
Sɛ hom rotweɔn ayɛ yie ana a,
Hom nnkɛba dabiarada;
Nnyɛ atsenenee a,
Abɔn na Jesus bɛfrɛe.

. Kobɔfo, ka w' ho, mma nnkyim;
Mbeamùdua n' ho wɔ kwan!
Hwehwɛ beà a woehyira do n':
Mbeamùdua n' ho wɔ kwan!
'Wo a wo kɔn ebu, aberɛ,
Jesus tum deda adwen;
Jesus tum deda adwen;
Hom wɔ w'Agyenkwa no mu:
Mbeamùdua n' ho wɔ nkwan!

. WƆMBƆ abɛn n' mu, wɔmbɔm',
Ahomkà awɔsѐ abɛn n';
Wɔmma amanaman ntse,
Nkɛpem wiadze ntuadze;
Afahodzi afe n' aba!
Hom a wɔapon hom, hom nsan mbra.

. Jesus, Sɔfopanyin,
Ɔaba werdam prɛko;
Sunsùm a wɔahaw, wɔnhom;
Awѐrɛfo ndzi dɛw,
Afahodzi afe n' aba!
Hom a wɔapon hom, hom nsan mbra.

. Wo dwuma dzi ma w' Agyenkwa
Na wo nkorafo adasa;
Yɛ ntsɛm, buber n' abɛn ampa;
Fonafo, rotweɔn ayɛ dɛn?

. Medze akomá a yaw ahyɛ n' má, 
Ewuradze na merefrɛ Wo;
W'adom ehumbɔbɔr ká pii;
Me Nyankopɔn, hu me mbɔbɔr.

. Motwe me nsa hwe mo bo do, 
Afɔdzi á ɔyɛ dur ahyɛ m' do;
Christ na Ne mbeamudua nye mo sú;
Me Nyankopɔn, hu me mbɔbɔr.

. Migyina ekyir nyinsu egur m' 
Munntum mma m'enyi do wɔ sor;
Wo na ihu me yaw nyina;
Me Nyankopɔn, hu me mbɔbɔr.

. Wiadze ntɔmpam', awartofo, 
Epoobɔfo, nwifo,hom ntsie!
Ɔrotweɔn ayɛ hom etuu;
Abɔn na N'adom gye hɔn sie;
Apaafo nnyi No ho hia;
Ɔbae bɛgyee dza 'ayew n' ara.

. Mber pii mo sunsum daduanyi
Daa bɔn mpokyerɛ na anago sum m';
W'enyiwa toow kan nserɛmɛn
Gyegyee fiadze hɔ, minyanee;
Mo mpokyerɛ gui, minyaa ahotɔ,
Mifiir edzi, midzii W'ekyir.

. Afei menya asaase pa a 
Medze me kra sekyɛ bɔto;
Jesus Ne pira a mo bɔn ntsi
Wɔdze piraa N' wiadze ahyɛse n';
Sor na asaase twam' kɔ mpo a,
N' ehumbɔbɔr betsim hɔ daa.

. Edze Wo nkwa maa me; 
Mo Wura, Wo bɔgyaa kyii
Ama aapon emi
Na meefi wum' masoɛr;
Edze Wo nkwa maa me:
'Midze, mama W' ebɛn?

. Mo Wura, dzi asɔw me ntsi 
Gyirama bi nnkotum ka;
Awerɛhow yerɛyerɛw
Ama eeyi m' efi hɛll;
Esɔɔw m'amandzehu:
Masɔw 'bɛn mama Wo?

. Ɔwo edze bɔnfakyɛ 
Na dɔ fi sor aba;
N-kwagye a odzi mu pii,
Edze ne nyina ama me;
Akyɛ me adze pii;
Mo so makyɛ W' ebɛn?

. Ewuradze ma furafo hu adze; 
Osuo adwen a ɔatɔ bitsim'
Ɔma tsibowa a ɔnnda asomdwee;
Ɔboa hɔho wɔ fona mu,
Kunafo nye egyanka so
Na ɔdom daduanyi fahodzi.

. Me kra, tsie! Ewuradze a; 
W'Agyenkwa na ɔrekasa n';
Tsie Ne ndze; ɔreka dɛ,
Bɔnyɛnyi, ana 'dɔ M' a?

. 'Mi na megyee w' fii mpokyerɛm', 
Meyɛɛ wo pira edur;
Eyewee n', mohwehwɛɛ wo;
Memaa wo sum daan ekan.

. Adom wie n'edwuma yɛ a, 
Ibohu M'enyimnyam ntsɛm;
Enye M'bɛtsena M'ahenguam';
Bɔnyɛnyi, ana 'dɔ M' a?

. Ese m' dɛ monhwehwɛ W'enyim; 
Dza mohwehwɛ ara nye n';
Dɛ m'bohu W'enyimnyam no,
Matse Wo ndze mo mu.l

. Bra, bɔsoɛ me! Mebue abow n' sesei; 
Mo Wura, minyim Wo ndze, dɛ Ɔwoara a.
Ewia atɔ dada na ehum reba;
Me Gyefo, ayɛ mbrɛ ebɔsoɛ me, bra!

. Jesus, n-kyɛ 'nye m' aanantsew 
Na meefi honam akwan do;
'Wo nye mo Kwan, yɛ m' Kwankyerɛfo;
Fa me nan si botan no do.

. Dɛ mbrɛ tsetse n' iyii Woho n'; 
Kyerɛw krɔnkrɔn bɔ Wo dzin dawur;
Ɔwo a ennsakyer ara da,
Fa W'ahentum kɛse n' bɛn hɛn.

. Fa wo sor akodze n' mia; 
Ma ɔnhyɛ wo daa nyina;
Ɔtamfo n' rehyɛ w' atsɛw:
                    Weɔn na sɔr.

. Gyaa mfɛfo bɔn agor,
Gyaa kasa bɔn nyina;
Dzi Nyame Ne dzin nyi,
Na mmfa nndzi agor;
Dwen na ma w'enyi mber,
Yɛ adɔyɛ, dzi nokwar;
Hwɛ Jesus ara daa,
Ɔdze w' bokodu.
Bisa Agyenkwa no hɔ mboa,
Ahoɔdzen nye akomatɔmu;
Ɔpe dɛ obɔboa wo,
Ɔdze w' bokodu.

. MEYƐ hɔho wɔ ha,
Sor nye me fie;
Asaase yέ awerɛhow,
Sor nye me fie;
Mbusu nye awerɛhow,
Etwa mo ho ehyia;
Ɔsor nye m'Egya kùrowm',
Sor nye me fie.

. Kaansa ehum rutù a,
Sor nye me fie;
M'akwantu ɔyɛ tsia,
Sor nye me fie;
Mber n'ehum nye me fie;
Ɔnnkyɛr na abɔ adze;
Na ewiei n' m'bokodu fie
Sor nye me fie.

. Metse sor man ho dɔ mu 'i, 
Munnsuro nsakyer biara;
M'awerɛhyɛmu yi dzi mu,
Biribiara nnsakyer ha;
Ehum botu abɔ m' ho aprɔw
M'akoma botu dze;
Na Nyame etwa moho ehyia 'i.
Ana m'bɛpa abaw?

. Beebiara a obegya me n'. 
Hia biara nnkɛsan me;
Mo Guanhwɛfo wɔ me nkyɛn,
Na minnkehia hweeara;
Ne nyansaa tse hɔ daa daa,
N'enyi nnyɛ kusuww da;
Onyim kwan a ɔfa do,
Na menye N' bɛnantsew.

. Asomdwee Hen!
Amanaman ruwu;
Wo mba a apon hɔn rotɔ akono.

. Adze nyinaa ne yɛ nnyɛ dzen mma  
Nyia otum gye Jesu dzin dzi;
Munngu Wo nokwar n' ho fi bio,
Mo Wura, megye n' dɔ mu ara;
Mutum, megye Wo dzi ampa,
Adze nyinaa ne yɛ nnyɛ dzen mma m'.

. Asaase nye hɛll gye kyim mpo a, 
Nyame N'asɛm nnkotwa apaw da;
Eguambaa n' beyi mo bɔn koraa,
Ampa, sɛ ɔyɛ dzen mpo a;
Dza ɔyɛ dzen mpo ɔbɛyɛ;
Adze nyina ne yɛ nnyɛ dzen mma m'.

. Nyame asomfo, hom nsoɛr! 
Asɔr no rotweɔn hom;
N'edwuma so ma n'hoɔdzen;
Hom nsoɛr, hom nhyɛ no dzen.

. Yɛ edwuma; hwer, ma woho nkɔm', 
Fa dɛw yɛ w'Egya N'edwuma;
Kwan a wo Wura duaa mu nye n';
Na 'wo, somfo, na ennkɛfa do?

. Meserɛ daadaa ahoɔdzen a 
Yebisa a hɛn nsa ka n'; 
Ɔnye adwen a onnhwinhwin
Na ɔka Woara ho daa;
Ɔdan mbrɛ mahyɛ W' enyimnyam
Mepen som biara do.

. Israel akodɔm Sahen, 
Sor akwantufo hɔn kwangyafo,
Wo nwinwin ase na yɛtse,
Wo dɔ mununkum kata hɛn do;
Hɛn tum, W'adom; hɛn mbra, W'asɛm;
Hɛn ewiei, Ewuradze N'enyimnyam.

. Agyenkwa, fa hɛn bɔn kyɛ hɛn; 
Hɛn mberɛwyɛ nyina Ɔwo nyim;
'Wo dzii hɛn kan nantseew wiadze,
'Wo tsee no mu yaw wenwen;
Eyɛɛ ankonam, dze berɛ,
Na fona kyiin sar no do.

. Gya m', O gya m', Jehovah tumfo, 
Kwantunyi a menam sar do;
Meyɛ mberɛw, 'wo yɛ hoɔdzenfo;
Fa Wo tum nsa n' suo mo mu;
Sor edziban!
Nyɛn me ndɛ na mber nyina.

. 'Wo a kitsa samanadze saafee
Akra a woenya Wo no wɔnnhwehwɛ hwee;
'Wo yɛ Nokwar, Ɔkwan, N-kwa ma abɔn;
Annkɔa -wɔnnkɔ Christ e, gya m' kodu sɔnn.

. Medan Wo gya a, mabra; adze ehu m';
Motwer Wo a, mewie, owu nnkotum me;
M'adagyaw mu, boa me menyɛ tartweɔn:
Ankor-n'apem-Nyame, gya m' kodu sɔnn,

. Hwɛ Jesus pa, mo nkwangye ntsi 
Na ebɛbraa adasa mu;
Mma nnto me seraha mma bɔn.

. Eku Woho ara ahwehwɛ m', 
Atɔ m' wɔ fona mbeamudua n' do;
Aso dɛm adom yi nyɛ gyan?

. Midzii fᴐ; medze nyinsuwa gye
M'enyimguasebra nyina tom';
Nyame, meserɛ W', fa mo ho kyɛ m'.

. Mifi m'akoma mu bu ntwɛr, 
Hwɛ, mo nnuho ayɛ dɛ nso;
Sɛ m'ewiei to m' a, ɔno boa m'.

. O nkwa a ɔahyɛ hɔn amaama a! 
Sor mframa a wɔgye n' yɛ dɛw;
Enyigye n' bor hɛn adwen do;
Onnyi kabea.

. EWÙRADZE a meda ho twer Wo,
'Besie m' nokwarm' akɔ ewiei;
Wo nokwar, Wo dɔ, nye Wo tum
Bɛgye m' akɔ me mber ewiei;
Sɛ moto honam yi ase a
'Dze kyɛw a ɔnnsɛɛ botua m' kaw.

. N-dɛ yɛ ekan da; 
Nyame, ma kan mbra ndɛ;
Hɛn Anapawi, hyerɛn hɛn do,
Na pam hɛn sum nyina.

. N-dɛ yɛ ahomgye da; 
Hyɛ hɛn ahoɔdzen mu;
Hue Wo bɔw nwinwin no ma hɛn,
Dwedwe 'koma a ɔahaw,

. N-dɛ yɛ asomdwee da; 
Fa W'asomdwee ma hɛn;
Ma mansotwe nyina mbɔ adze 
Ma wongyaa n-tokwaa.

. Agyenkwa Christ, Nyimpa nye W' so; 
Wɔatseetsee Wo, wɔasɔ W' ahwɛ;
Ema Wo dɔ enyi do a, ihu
Epirakur a fɛr dze rusuma n'.

. Nyame, fa Wo nhyira gya hɛn kwan, 
Dom hɛn dɛw na asomdwee;
Ma ankorankor yennya Wo dɔ
Mfa ndzi nkwagye adom ho dɛw;
Ao, hyɛ hɛn dzen
Wɔ bra sar akwantu yim'.

. Ma ne ndze nyɛ wansa daa; 
Ɔmbɔ nkaa wɔ atsɛmbu ho;
Ɔnka Agyenkwa pa ho nsɛm,
Yɛserɛ Wo, tsie hɛn.

. Tsetsew ne nkyehoma mu; 
Tseam ma ko na 'nyiber ngyaa;
Dom no ɔsor asomdwee n',
Yɛserɛ Wo, tsie hɛn.

. Honam a wobuu mbɔbɔrhu mu',
Bɔgya a wokyii mbɔbɔrhu mu';
Ɔwo na ekaa nkwa asɛm no,
Ɔwo ewu ma hɛn bɔn ewu;

. Jesus a wɔasera No n' na hwɛ N'enyim, 
Ehwɛ hɛn a, hwɛ hɛn wɔ Christ no mu;
Mma nnhwɛ hɛn dɛ yeetsiatsia W'adom do;
Mma nnhwɛ hɛn mpaabɔ nye gyedzi nwinwin n':
Na hwɛ! hɛn mfom nye hɔn ho akatua,
Wo Ba, hɛn Wura, N'amandzehu so ntam'.

. Hɔn so a yɛdɔ hɔn kyɛn adze nyina n', 
Yedua Christ do yɛtotɔ serɛ ma hɔn;
O fa W'ehumbɔbɔr fua hɔn Wo bom',
Bɔ mbɔdzen nyina hɔn kra ne yie ho;
Sie hɔn krɔnn fi emumuyɛ nkekaa ho,
Fa dzenhyɛ wie dwuma n' ma wɔnkɔ kan.

. Fa W'adom mbordo n oma hɛn,
Ɔnsera hɛn, ɔntsew hɛn enyim;
Pam atamfo, ma asomdwee;
Mbrɛ ewɔ mbusu nntum mmba hɔ.

. Fa Wo nsa to me tsir do;
Ma menda W'abaw no mu;
Ma montwer Woara Wo bom';
Mo Wura, boaboa m' ma menda

. Mbofra hɛn fasusu nye No, 
Onyinii dɛ hɛnara,
Kakrabaa, m-berɛmberɛw;
Osui, serewee dɛ hɛnara;
Ntsi hɛn yaw ɔtse ma hɛn,
Na hɛn dɛw onyam' kyɛpɛn.

. Ewuradze, fa Wo nhyira dom hɛn, 
Yebehyia mu bio wɔ ha;
Ma yentu anamɔn nkɔ kan
Wɔ Wo dɔ, gyedzi na surom';
Bɔ hɛn ho ban
Dɛ ebɛn hɛn daa nyina.

. Nyame fa Wo nhyira gya hɛn kwan,
Yɛda ase na ehumbɔbɔr;
Fa nnuhofo nyina mfom kyɛ hɔn;
Wonnya mber mfa ntsen dza asɛɛ n'
Na mma Wo mba
Mmfom Wo Sunsum ara bio.

. Egya baatan, kora hɔn a 
Worinnhyia mu bio wɔ ha;
Ma dza woedua n' nsow aba pa
Bafuu ofi ber to ber;
Hɔn a wɔresan n'
Nnyɛ anokwafo nsen nkan' n'.  Amen.

. AMAN Wurà a W' adom dɔɔ sõ,
Wo nkὸwaà atɔbɔ tonton Wo dzin;
Ayɛ hɛn man n' Apatasu;
Wo tum nwanwa fir mbersantsen.
Asɛɛ tamfo n' mamman;
Agye hɛn so hɛn man;
Aman-suro Nyame,
'Wo nye mbɔbɔrhunyi.
Yehuhor Wo, Ɔnwanwanyi!

. Mber a asɛɛ n' kwa hyɛ ananm'; 
Bɔ bra dɛ ndɛ owu nam kwanm';
Kɔ kan kora akyɛdze a Nyame ama n';
Siesie woho ma atsɛmbu da n'.

. Fa nokwar ka w' asɛm biara; 
Mma wo tsibowa mmbu w' atsɛn da;
Nyame enyi hu mbea nyina do
Hyɛ nsumaam' adwen nye nyɛe nsew;

. N-kwa da ketseaba yi rotwe kɔ; 
Wiadze dɛw repa; n' enyimnyam resen;
N-sakyer na ɔsɛɛ nko ara na muhu;
Ao, 'Wo a ennsakyer da, enye me ntsena.

. Egya, ehu hɛn mbɔbɔr pɛn;
Na 'da ho hwɛ hɛn;
Mbrɛ yɛtse, dza yɛwɔ biara,
Yedua Christ do dze ma W'.

. Nyame, ndɔbaa Wura,
Tsie Wo mba mpaayi;
Hɛn nkwa nyina fir Woara;
Gye hɛn ayɛyi.

. Abɔdze biara nya N' akɔndɔdze;
Nam, nnoma na hambowa nyina so;
Ɔkyɛso Nyame ma wonya wodzi,
Ntsi wohuhor Ne dzin afebɔɔ.

. Hɔ na hɛn nyinsuwa bɔ adze; 
Hɔ na wɔkyerɛ hɛn ase;
Hɔ na ɔsɛndzifo pa n'
Hwɛ hɛn bra nyinara mu:
